  "output_data": ["Structured Requirement Data (Intent: Initialize Story; Entities: 汐颜, Gotham; Emotional Target: Arrival atmosphere; Potential Thematic Flags: Travel, Gotham Atmosphere)", "Refined Engagement Depth Score (Medium - Narrative introduction needed)"]
