  "primary_agent": "Hermes",
  "function": "Constructs blueprint: Scene: Damp alley near Gotham Harbor. Time: Night. Weather: Foggy/Drizzling (implied). Action: 汐颜 materializes/stands. Focus: Sensory details (smell, sound, sight, touch - specify: brine, decay, distant sirens, damp cold, wet cobblestones, flickering neon). Character: Describe 汐颜's appearance contrast, calm observation, subtle hexagram shimmer (ambiguous). Conclude: Sound of shattering glass nearby. Emotion: Disorientation mixed with calm curiosity. 'Show, Don't Tell' instructions: Show the environment through sensory details, show her calm demeanor through lack of panic.",
